<TEXT>
   Former Watergate prosecutor Archibald Cox has
declined to take over as chief of the state's ethics panel but will
advise Gov. Michael S. Dukakis on a number of ethics issue.
   Cox, a Harvard Law School professor and chairman of the citizens
